com.baasbox.android

Class BaasResult<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.baasbox.android.BaasResult<T>

  • public abstract class BaasResult<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the result of a BaasBox request. It can be either a successful response or a failure due to an error or an user cancellation.
    Since:
    0.7.3
